Description: Wasta-Linux XFCE Customization for 20.04 Focal Fossa
 XFCE desktop setup for Wasta-Linux. Default layout in etc/xdg/xdg-xfce gives
 a basic Windows XP-like experience. The wasta-xfce-layout utility can be used
 to choose other desktop layouts such as Wasta-Redmond7, Wasta-Cupertino, and
 Wasta-Unity. These additional layouts rely on the xfce4-dockbarx-plugin for
 the xfce4-panel.
 .
 Nemo is set as the default file manager and will draw desktop icons due
 to wasta-multidesktop settings.
